<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>🌟 IQC Retest and FA Tracking System 🌟</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body class="p-4 md:p-6">
    <div class="relative min-h-screen">
        <div id="main-content" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-6 app-container p-6 rounded-2xl">
            
            <div class="demo-notice">
                <i data-lucide="info" class="w-5 h-5 inline mr-2"></i>
                📌 線上測試環境 | Online Test Environment - 數據存儲於瀏覽器本地
            </div>

            <header class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-white">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                    <i data-lucide="clipboard-check" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
                    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold" id="app-title">🌟 IQC Retest & FA Tracking 🌟</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mt-2 md:mt-0 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
                    <i data-lucide="languages" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    <span class="text-sm font-medium" id="lang-label">Language:</span>
                    <select id="lang-selector" class="bg-white/90 text-gray-800 rounded-md border-0 shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white px-3 py-1">
                        <option value="繁體中文">繁體中文</option>
                        <option value="English">English</option>
                        <option value="Tiếng Việt">Tiếng Việt</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </header>

            <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-4 rounded-lg">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <i data-lucide="lightbulb" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-1">快速測試指南 Quick Guide</h3>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-blue-700 space-y-1">
                            <li>✅ 填寫所有必填欄位後點擊「儲存」Fill all required fields and click "Save"</li>
                            <li>✅ 當 Is RTV = Yes 時，點擊「查看 RTV 信息」按鈕 Click "View RTV Info" when Is RTV = Yes</li>
                            <li>✅ 管理員密碼 Admin password：<code class="bg-blue-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-mono">11011163</code></li>
                            <li>✅ 資料自動保存到本地 Data auto-saves to browser localStorage</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-card bg-white p-6 border-l-4 border-indigo-500">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4">
                    <i data-lucide="file-plus" class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600"></i>
                    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800" id="form-title">新增 Retest 紀錄</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                    <div>
                        <label for="qpn" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1" id="label-qpn">
                            <span class="flex items-center"><i data-lucide="package" class="w-4 h-4 mr-1"></i>料號QPN <span class="text-red-500 ml-1">*</span></span>
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" id="qpn" list="qpn-suggestions" class="block w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500" placeholder="例如: QPN-2025-001">
                        <datalist id="qpn-suggestions"></datalist>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="sn" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1" id="label-sn">
                            <span class="flex items-center"><i data-lucide="hash" class="w-4 h-4 mr-1"></i>SN <span class="text-red-500 ml-1">*</span></span>
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" id="sn" class="block w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500" placeholder="例如: SN123456789">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="dept" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1" id="label-dept">
                            <span class="flex items-center"><i data-lucide="building" class="w-4 h-4 mr-1"></i>部門 <span class="text-red-500 ml-1">*</span></span>
                        </label>
                        <select id="dept" class="block w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500">
                            <option value="">--請選擇--</option>
                            <option>PE</option>
                            <option>SQE</option>
                            <option>PD</option>
                            <option>EE</option>
                            <option>Others</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="requester" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1" id="label-requester">
                            <span class="flex items-center"><i data-lucide="user" class="w-4 h-4 mr-1"></i>人員 <span class="text-red-500 ml-1">*</span></span>
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" id="requester" list="requester-suggestions" class="block w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500" placeholder="s911986">
                        <datalist id="requester-suggestions"></datalist>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="verifier" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1" id="label-verifier">
                            <span class="flex items-center"><i data-lucide="user-check" class="w-4 h-4 mr-1"></i>驗證人員 <span class="text-red-500 ml-1">*</span></span>
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" id="verifier" list="verifier-suggestions" class="block w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500" placeholder="驗證人員名稱">
                        <datalist id="verifier-suggestions"></datalist>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="result" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1" id="label-result">
                            <span class="flex items-center"><i data-lucide="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 mr-1"></i>結果 <span class="text-red-500 ml-1">*</span></span>
                        </label>
                        <select id="result" class="block w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500">
                            <option value="">--請選擇--</option>
                            <option>Pass</option>
                            <option>NG</option>
                            <option>Not Test</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-card bg-white p-6">
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-4 justify-between items-start lg:items-center">
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 items-start sm:items-end w-full lg:w-auto">
                        <div>
                            <label for="start_date" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1" id="label-start_date">
                                <i data-lucide="calendar" class="w-4 h-4 inline mr-1"></i>開始日期
                            </label>
                            <input type="date" id="start_date" class="block w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label for="end_date" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1" id="label-end_date">
                                <i data-lucide="calendar" class="w-4 h-4 inline mr-1"></i>結束日期
                            </label>
                            <input type="date" id="end_date" class="block w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500">
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-2">
                            <button id="filter-btn" class="flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-lg shadow-sm text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-all">
                                <i data-lucide="filter" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2"></i><span id="btn-filter">篩選</span>
                            </button>
                            <button id="clear-filter-btn" class="flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg shadow-sm text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 transition-all">
                                <i data-lucide="rotate-cw" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2"></i><span id="btn-clear_filter">清除</span>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-start lg:justify-end w-full lg:w-auto">
                        <button id="save-btn" class="flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg text-white bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 transition-all shadow-md hover:shadow-lg">
                            <i data-lucide="save" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2"></i><span id="btn-save">儲存</span>
                        </button>
                        <button id="export-btn" class="flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg text-white bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-700 transition-all shadow-md hover:shadow-lg">
                            <i data-lucide="download" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2"></i><span id="btn-export">匯出</span>
                        </button>
                        <button id="delete-btn" class="flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg text-white bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 transition-all shadow-md hover:shadow-lg">
                            <i data-lucide="trash-2" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2"></i><span id="btn-delete">刪除選中</span>
                        </button>
                        <button id="search-btn" class="flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg text-white bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-800 transition-all shadow-md hover:shadow-lg">
                            <i data-lucide="search" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2"></i><span id="btn-search">搜尋 SN</span>
                        </button>
                        <button id="admin-btn" class="flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg text-white bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 transition-all shadow-md hover:shadow-lg">
                            <i data-lucide="shield" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2"></i><span id="btn-admin">管理員模式</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="table-card bg-white overflow-hidden">
                <div class="table-container border rounded-lg">
                    <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200">
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th scope="col" class="p-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-white uppercase tracking-wider">
                                    <input type="checkbox" id="select-all-checkbox" class="rounded border-white/30">
                                </th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody class="bg-white divide-y divide-gray-200" id="records-table-body"></tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>

            <footer class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600 px-2 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 rounded-lg">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                    <i data-lucide="info" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    <div id="status-bar">準備就緒。</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                    <i data-lucide="database" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    <div id="record-count">筆數統計: 0</div>
                </div>
            </footer>
        </div>

        <div id="modal-template" class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4 modal-backdrop hidden">
            <div class="modal-content bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-md p-6 transform scale-95">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b pb-3 mb-4">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900" id="modal-title">Modal Title</h3>
                    <button id="modal-close-btn" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="x" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div id="modal-body"></div>
                <div class="mt-6 flex justify-end space-x-3" id="modal-footer"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
